From: patch-rebuild <patches@local>
Subject: [PATCH] topic5: LINEAR DmaBuf CUDA-EGL + loud mmap_cuda fallback

Prefer eglCreateImage + cuGraphicsEGLRegisterImage (no GL convert shaders).
On failure: ERROR log convert_path=mmap_cuda, mmap→CUDA upload, and
stream_stats encode_target_residency=cpu so WebUI is not "gpu native".
cuImportExternalMemory removed (always fails on gamescope portal FDs).

